I"Ó<p>Phantom Chess is an <strong>auto-chess</strong> game built for <a href="https://itch.io/jam/geta-game-jam-8">Geta Game Jam 8</a>. The player plays against the AI and tries to reach the highest level they can. The game goes on till the player loses. It functions as a regular auto-chess game where the player can buy/sell units, upgrade them via combining 3, and more.
